        "testo_it": "Mojtaba Khamenei nominato leader iraniano; Israele bombarda Teheran.",
        "priorita": "Altissima",
        "id_gruppo": 1,
        "link": "https://www.aljazeera.com/news/liveblog/2026/3/9/iran-war-live-mojtaba-khamenei-named-supreme-leader-israel-bombs-tehran?traffic_source=rss",
